WEBVTT

00:21.184 --> 00:22.464
â™ªThat dayâ™ª

00:22.880 --> 00:24.448
â™ªNothing stays together foreverâ™ª

00:24.448 --> 00:25.792
â™ªI've quit romanceâ™ª

00:26.218 --> 00:27.920
â™ªWho hasn't failed againâ™ª

00:27.920 --> 00:31.424
â™ªCrying in deathâ™ª

00:31.424 --> 00:34.016
â™ªAnd in lifeâ™ª

00:34.432 --> 00:36.370
â™ªEven nowâ™ª

00:36.672 --> 00:38.656
â™ªWe keep learningâ™ª

00:38.656 --> 00:39.680
â™ªIt's no surpriseâ™ª

00:39.744 --> 00:42.144
â™ªBeing happy is so hardâ™ª

00:42.144 --> 00:43.968
â™ªWeirdly, I became a role modelâ™ª

00:44.736 --> 00:46.688
â™ªOn the day we met again, we said hiâ™ª

00:46.688 --> 00:52.896
â™ªIt was a reminder,
a test, and a complaintâ™ª

00:52.896 --> 00:56.003
â™ªWho can do anything without regretâ™ª

00:56.003 --> 00:59.424
â™ªI am all rightâ™ª

01:00.480 --> 01:05.074
â™ªMay you live in peaceâ™ª

01:05.074 --> 01:07.456
â™ªLet the world roarâ™ª

01:07.456 --> 01:09.732
â™ªSounds like a carnivalâ™ª

01:09.732 --> 01:14.453
â™ªBeing alive is never dullâ™ª

01:14.453 --> 01:18.830
â™ªHow wonderful to be freeâ™ª

01:18.830 --> 01:23.485
â™ªI became even better without youâ™ª

01:23.485 --> 01:25.824
â™ªNothing can be perfectâ™ª

01:25.824 --> 01:28.224
â™ªWe bless each other in painâ™ª

01:28.224 --> 01:34.234
â™ªWe nod and smileâ™ª

01:35.328 --> 01:36.288
â™ªMay we both be wellâ™ª

01:36.288 --> 01:41.024
= Love's Ambition=

01:41.181 --> 01:43.961
=Episode 19=

01:48.893 --> 01:49.572
Yao.

01:49.973 --> 01:51.013
Take a break.

01:52.093 --> 01:53.132
Let's talk about

01:53.132 --> 01:55.212
the makeup and the clothing

01:55.253 --> 01:56.173
for the next episode.

01:59.052 --> 01:59.653
What's wrong?

02:00.373 --> 02:01.492
Why are you down?

02:02.653 --> 02:05.412
We've been spending on fabrics

02:05.492 --> 02:06.733
and filming equipment

02:06.932 --> 02:08.132
like water flowing.

02:08.892 --> 02:09.973
Our startup funds

02:11.132 --> 02:12.253
are almost gone.

02:13.533 --> 02:15.692
I just feel that you trusted me so much,

02:15.852 --> 02:17.012
but the videos we posted

02:17.412 --> 02:18.813
got zero response.

02:19.493 --> 02:22.213
I feel terribly guilty.

02:24.692 --> 02:26.132
Snap out of it.

02:26.132 --> 02:27.653
Stop overthinking.

02:27.773 --> 02:29.132
You're our stylist.

02:29.172 --> 02:31.412
Just focus on making good outfits.

02:31.412 --> 02:32.933
Don't worry about anything else.

02:32.933 --> 02:34.012
We'll handle them.

02:34.093 --> 02:34.653
Got it?

02:37.012 --> 02:38.053
Then I'll keep trying.

02:38.773 --> 02:40.253
Not a single stitch will be wasted.

02:41.213 --> 02:42.412
You were saying?

02:43.253 --> 02:43.973
Here's the thing.

02:44.373 --> 02:45.412
Take a look.

02:45.852 --> 02:47.053
Pick from these.

02:47.412 --> 02:49.093
I also brought many lipsticks

02:49.692 --> 02:51.053
for you to pick.

02:52.132 --> 02:54.132
We'll only expand our consumer base

02:54.132 --> 02:56.452
after building brand awareness.

02:56.813 --> 02:58.213
Many college students

02:58.213 --> 02:59.612
and young customers

02:59.612 --> 03:01.933
are fond of ethnic-style accessories.

03:02.172 --> 03:02.933
Let's take a look

03:02.933 --> 03:05.292
at our overall design philosophy.

03:06.053 --> 03:07.093
As you can see,

03:07.093 --> 03:08.892
we want ethnic clothing

03:08.933 --> 03:10.172
to shine globally

03:10.172 --> 03:11.132
and make an impact.

03:11.493 --> 03:13.933
We've also conducted some research.

03:14.053 --> 03:16.012
Young girl around 20

03:16.053 --> 03:17.892
now prefer ethnic outfits,

03:17.892 --> 03:19.412
including Chinese-style clothing.

03:20.012 --> 03:21.172
Mr. Wang, Mr. Zhang, Mr. Li.

03:21.333 --> 03:23.653
We've prepared a presentation.

03:23.973 --> 03:26.012
We target ethnic-style apparel

03:26.053 --> 03:27.292
with customized designs.

03:27.493 --> 03:28.933
This is to you. Cheers.

03:30.572 --> 03:31.292
Office workers.

03:31.612 --> 03:32.933
This design...

03:33.452 --> 03:35.373
It has modern styling...

03:39.132 --> 03:40.612
It's highly adaptable.

03:42.612 --> 03:44.493
It makes a fashionable daily wear.

04:14.373 --> 04:14.933
Hello?

04:15.213 --> 04:15.933
Mr. Ding?

04:17.893 --> 04:18.732
This is Xu Yan.

04:18.773 --> 04:19.292
Yeah.

04:19.653 --> 04:20.693
Nothing urgent.

04:20.773 --> 04:21.812
I just wanted to

04:22.213 --> 04:24.372
ask about the proposal I sent you.

04:25.372 --> 04:27.093
Please review it

04:27.172 --> 04:28.932
when you have time. Thank you.

04:29.333 --> 04:30.252
If you're interested,

04:30.573 --> 04:33.172
I'll visit your office for details.

04:34.352 --> 04:36.464
â™ªPassing through my eyes
a thousand timesâ™ª

04:36.653 --> 04:38.412
No worries.

04:40.492 --> 04:40.932
Okay.

04:41.333 --> 04:41.812
Got it.

04:43.492 --> 04:44.252
No problem.

04:44.720 --> 04:46.763
â™ªWhen you speak, the universe haltsâ™ª

04:46.763 --> 04:49.497
â™ªEven fate grows stillâ™ª

04:50.567 --> 04:52.702
â™ªSunset glow caressesâ™ª

04:53.834 --> 04:56.288
â™ªYour silhouetteâ™ª

04:57.904 --> 04:59.856
â™ªTill sunset takes dreams awayâ™ª

04:59.856 --> 05:02.288
â™ªLeaving me, unbrokenâ™ª

05:03.536 --> 05:05.232
â™ªEnvying dustâ™ª

05:06.224 --> 05:09.048
â™ªResting in your heartâ™ª

05:10.960 --> 05:12.795
â™ªLike fireworks that lovedâ™ª

05:12.795 --> 05:14.288
â™ªRushing toward the starsâ™ª

05:14.288 --> 05:16.427
â™ªUndaunted by painâ™ª

05:17.456 --> 05:19.323
â™ªFearless of flamesâ™ª

05:20.412 --> 05:21.653
(I just want to)

05:21.693 --> 05:22.932
(correct my mistakes)

05:24.492 --> 05:26.812
and live my life properly.

05:30.412 --> 05:32.052
Since we've decided to divorce,

05:35.372 --> 05:37.013
let's be strangers then.

05:42.133 --> 05:43.653
The screen is broken again.

05:55.052 --> 05:55.732
Shen Haoming.

05:58.852 --> 05:59.653
Why are you here?

06:04.333 --> 06:05.492
I came to check on Yan.

06:06.732 --> 06:07.333
Save it.

06:09.533 --> 06:12.252
I feel like
speaking for my sister today.

06:13.133 --> 06:15.093
She did make mistakes,

06:15.133 --> 06:17.013
but you're not so innocent, either.

06:18.292 --> 06:19.052
She tried so hard

06:19.773 --> 06:21.252
to save your relationship.

06:21.252 --> 06:22.492
But what did you do?

06:23.013 --> 06:24.693
Now she's running around,

06:24.693 --> 06:25.693
securing investments.

06:26.133 --> 06:27.773
If you'd treated her better,

06:27.773 --> 06:29.812
she wouldn't have ended up like this.

06:30.093 --> 06:31.252
Now you're being nice?

06:31.252 --> 06:32.333
That's unnecessary.

06:34.773 --> 06:37.693
I want to help her,
but she keeps refusing.

06:38.693 --> 06:39.492
Please talk to her.

06:39.852 --> 06:41.372
No, I won't.

06:43.492 --> 06:44.812
She won't take

06:44.812 --> 06:45.932
another penny from you.

06:46.893 --> 06:47.973
You should just leave.

06:48.333 --> 06:49.492
And don't come back.

07:02.533 --> 07:03.412
Ms. Xu,

07:03.812 --> 07:05.533
the popularity and views of your videos

07:05.732 --> 07:07.932
haven't met our expectations.

07:08.172 --> 07:10.533
We will sit on your proposal for now.

07:10.800 --> 07:13.573
Alright, thank you, Mr. Zhang.
Looking forward to working with you.

07:13.573 --> 07:14.052
Alright.

07:14.492 --> 07:15.773
Same here.

07:29.893 --> 07:30.492
Ms. Xu.

07:34.412 --> 07:35.213
Mr. Jiang Liang.

07:36.252 --> 07:37.093
Call me Mr. Liang.

07:38.252 --> 07:38.773
Mr. Liang.

07:39.492 --> 07:40.336
What a coincidence.

07:41.052 --> 07:42.492
I have meetings scheduled here

07:42.693 --> 07:44.013
for some venture projects.

07:44.852 --> 07:46.172
Are you here

07:46.893 --> 07:48.292
for some promising ventures?

07:49.573 --> 07:50.453
Share the information

07:50.453 --> 07:51.252
if you don't mind.

07:51.984 --> 07:53.872
(Yan Studio)

07:54.013 --> 07:55.492
I'm seeking funding.

07:55.932 --> 07:56.693
Seeking funding?

07:58.172 --> 07:58.693
You?

08:02.133 --> 08:02.612
Yes, me.

08:03.773 --> 08:05.052
Ms. Xu, you must be joking.

08:05.932 --> 08:06.932
I'm dead serious.

08:07.812 --> 08:08.412
Really.

08:09.492 --> 08:11.052
So the rumors are true.

08:11.812 --> 08:13.773
You and Shen Haoming fell out.

08:20.292 --> 08:22.013
That's irrelevant.

08:24.533 --> 08:25.773
What's your project about?

08:38.492 --> 08:39.813
Fashion-related short videos.

08:40.732 --> 08:41.852
We aim to expand into

08:41.852 --> 08:43.012
offline garment production.

08:43.612 --> 08:44.252
Short videos?

08:46.813 --> 08:48.492
Why enter such saturated waters?

08:50.372 --> 08:51.093
Mr. Jiang Liang...

08:51.612 --> 08:52.053
Sorry.

08:52.532 --> 08:53.213
Mr. Liang.

08:54.093 --> 08:55.132
Any thoughts?

08:56.933 --> 08:59.053
Statistically speaking, I'm pessimistic.

08:59.693 --> 09:01.053
By Q2 this year,

09:01.413 --> 09:02.372
there are 1.55 billion

09:02.573 --> 09:03.492
short video accounts

09:03.492 --> 09:05.213
across major platforms.

09:06.693 --> 09:07.652
There are 15.08 million

09:07.693 --> 09:08.973
professional streamers,

09:09.252 --> 09:11.732
500,000 accounts with 100K fans,

09:12.132 --> 09:13.852
40,000 with a million fans,

09:14.093 --> 09:16.693
and just 1,000
with 10 million followers.

09:17.892 --> 09:19.612
You want to stand out

09:19.612 --> 09:21.892
in 80 million daily uploads?

09:21.892 --> 09:22.933
All I can say is

09:24.973 --> 09:25.732
good luck.

09:27.892 --> 09:29.093
Impressive, Mr. Liang.

09:30.372 --> 09:32.053
You're very well-informed.

09:36.652 --> 09:38.732
Now, your design is not bad.

09:39.693 --> 09:42.333
It fuses ethnic and avant-garde styles.

09:43.453 --> 09:44.012
But

09:45.892 --> 09:46.732
it lacks uniqueness.

09:47.532 --> 09:49.132
The execution is superficial.

09:49.333 --> 09:50.213
It lacks soul.

09:50.573 --> 09:51.612
My rule is

09:52.132 --> 09:54.173
better risky than boring.

09:57.492 --> 09:58.213
No offense.

09:59.173 --> 10:00.132
That's just me.

10:00.772 --> 10:01.532
Straight talker.

10:01.612 --> 10:02.333
No offense taken.

10:03.573 --> 10:05.012
Your comment is constructive.

10:06.252 --> 10:07.213
I agree.

10:08.053 --> 10:09.492
To get investors,

10:10.693 --> 10:11.693
work on three essentials:

10:12.532 --> 10:13.372
thorough research,

10:14.173 --> 10:15.053
clear strengths,

10:15.532 --> 10:16.492
and absolute execution.

10:17.293 --> 10:18.693
But most people

10:18.892 --> 10:20.693
obsess over the idea alone.

10:21.532 --> 10:22.852
Their approach is wrong.

10:23.612 --> 10:26.252
If we don't emphasize
project-specific context,

10:26.333 --> 10:27.333
what should we address?

10:29.892 --> 10:30.492
The investors.

10:32.892 --> 10:34.053
The investors?

10:35.492 --> 10:36.772
Every investment firm

10:36.772 --> 10:38.213
has its own philosophy

10:38.293 --> 10:39.372
and key focus areas.

10:40.573 --> 10:43.813
Some value accurate
market understanding,

10:44.413 --> 10:46.492
others emphasize unique selling points,

10:46.573 --> 10:48.693
while some focus on your execution.

10:49.252 --> 10:51.162
Therefore, you must tailor
your proposals

10:51.162 --> 10:53.333
according to the priorities

10:53.372 --> 10:55.093
of each investment firm.

10:55.892 --> 10:59.213
That ensures higher success rates.

11:12.772 --> 11:13.612
Thank you.

11:15.652 --> 11:16.933
Don't be discouraged, though.

11:17.612 --> 11:19.012
It's a solid project.

11:19.333 --> 11:20.612
Make proper adjustments.

11:21.813 --> 11:22.852
It will work.

11:26.933 --> 11:27.612
Mr. Liang,

11:28.813 --> 11:31.173
from an investor's perspective,

11:32.973 --> 11:34.213
would you fund this project?

11:36.012 --> 11:37.492
In its current state,

11:43.173 --> 11:43.772
I wouldn't.

11:45.772 --> 11:46.693
But I can bring you

11:46.693 --> 11:47.813
a great photographer

11:47.813 --> 11:48.933
who's my friend.

11:50.012 --> 11:51.492
My connection comes free.

11:53.492 --> 11:54.053
Thank you.

11:54.413 --> 11:55.973
No problem. It's nothing.

11:58.492 --> 11:59.173
Let me add you

12:00.772 --> 12:01.492
on WeChat.

12:02.173 --> 12:02.732
Alright.

12:04.813 --> 12:05.648
I'll scan your code.

12:06.492 --> 12:07.053
Done.

12:11.132 --> 12:11.933
Mr. Shen,

12:12.612 --> 12:14.933
many executives couldn't believe that

12:15.492 --> 12:17.213
the Cheng'an County project
made a comeback.

12:17.532 --> 12:19.492
Hongyun is notorious.

12:19.892 --> 12:22.053
Nobody wants to deal with it.

12:22.492 --> 12:23.252
But this time,

12:23.492 --> 12:26.053
you solved the problems impressively.

12:26.573 --> 12:28.933
This project has been revitalized.

12:29.213 --> 12:30.132
So what?

12:30.693 --> 12:32.732
I'm still sidelined.

12:32.973 --> 12:34.933
Don't you already have a plan?

12:35.933 --> 12:38.213
The Baraikins will arrive in Jingzhou

12:38.492 --> 12:39.772
for vacation at Yanbo Resort.

12:41.492 --> 12:42.093
Golden paint.

12:48.173 --> 12:49.612
Jinda's overseas expansion

12:50.372 --> 12:51.813
has long sought cooperation with

12:51.813 --> 12:53.252
this Russian real estate tycoon.

12:53.892 --> 12:55.093
It's a great opportunity.

12:55.252 --> 12:56.132
But someone

12:56.772 --> 12:58.173
might've beaten us to it.

12:59.892 --> 13:00.933
Situo Construction?

13:02.132 --> 13:05.492
They assigned someone named Steve to
speak to the Baraikins.

13:06.732 --> 13:08.492
Let him be the vanguard.

13:10.492 --> 13:11.173
Done.

13:12.252 --> 13:12.852
Chen Lin.

13:13.333 --> 13:14.252
I composed this

13:14.492 --> 13:17.973
from 2,441 pieces of agave leaves.

13:18.093 --> 13:18.732
Impressive?

13:27.053 --> 13:27.652
Cool.

13:48.132 --> 13:48.892
Thank you.

13:51.012 --> 13:51.813
Mr. Baraikin,

13:52.252 --> 13:55.053
if you're willing to cooperate with us,

13:55.413 --> 13:57.973
you can not only enjoy the investment,

13:59.252 --> 14:00.333
our company...

14:01.293 --> 14:01.892
It's okay.

14:02.372 --> 14:03.612
Let's speak Chinese.

14:06.053 --> 14:07.693
Your Chinese proficiency surprises me.

14:07.973 --> 14:09.093
My wife is Chinese.

14:09.933 --> 14:12.053
We speak Chinese at home.

14:12.973 --> 14:13.892
Excellent.

14:14.173 --> 14:15.173
I'll continue in Chinese.

14:15.413 --> 14:15.892
Go ahead.

14:16.252 --> 14:17.053
I meant to say

14:17.372 --> 14:18.772
that if you collaborate with us,

14:19.093 --> 14:20.573
we'll increase investment

14:20.813 --> 14:21.732
and prioritize you

14:22.012 --> 14:23.973
as our crucial
overseas strategic partner.

14:24.573 --> 14:25.892
I'd consider your proposal.

14:27.132 --> 14:28.372
I'll enjoy the vacation

14:28.492 --> 14:29.413
with my wife in China.

14:29.892 --> 14:30.813
After that,

14:31.053 --> 14:33.333
I can visit Situo for business.

14:34.492 --> 14:35.173
Excellent.

14:35.652 --> 14:38.333
May I ask about your plans in China?

14:39.492 --> 14:40.532
If you don't mind,

14:40.892 --> 14:41.973
I could be your guide.

14:42.693 --> 14:43.372
Thank you.

14:43.693 --> 14:46.453
But our itinerary has already been set.

14:46.772 --> 14:47.693
Besides,

14:47.892 --> 14:49.372
I promised my wife

14:49.372 --> 14:50.372
not to talk business

14:50.732 --> 14:51.973
during the vacation.

14:53.573 --> 14:54.892
As you please.

14:55.333 --> 14:56.652
I wish you a pleasant holiday.

14:59.652 --> 15:02.492
I bet you're still single.

15:03.413 --> 15:04.093
Yeah.

15:04.693 --> 15:06.288
Once you get married, you'll realize

15:06.372 --> 15:08.772
that career is just
a small part of life.

15:09.252 --> 15:10.693
A man's achievement is measured

15:10.732 --> 15:12.652
not by wealth nor status,

15:13.012 --> 15:15.492
but by the home he builds.

15:15.612 --> 15:16.093
Here.

15:17.213 --> 15:18.693
To men with families.

15:19.012 --> 15:19.612
Thank you.

15:20.093 --> 15:22.732
Mr. Baraikin values family deeply.

15:23.053 --> 15:25.492
He believes a man who cherishes

15:25.813 --> 15:27.573
and cares for his wife

15:27.772 --> 15:30.173
is truly wise, committed,

15:30.532 --> 15:31.852
and a trustworthy partner.

15:48.848 --> 15:53.136
(Yan)

15:55.600 --> 16:00.080
(Yan)

16:20.293 --> 16:21.053
Look.

16:29.813 --> 16:30.852
The sleeves are uneven.

16:30.933 --> 16:32.573
And here.

16:41.492 --> 16:42.173
Have some coffee.

16:42.973 --> 16:43.732
Thank you.

16:44.413 --> 16:46.492
How do you like
the shooting environment?

16:47.333 --> 16:48.053
It's great.

16:48.732 --> 16:49.973
Thank you for your support.

16:51.012 --> 16:51.573
Mr. Liang,

16:51.612 --> 16:52.652
since you're in a hurry,

16:52.973 --> 16:54.173
I've adjusted the order

16:54.173 --> 16:55.213
of the shooting.

16:55.372 --> 16:56.453
Let me brief you.

16:57.132 --> 16:59.852
We plan to start with the second set.

16:59.852 --> 17:01.532
The AC is strong. Don't catch a cold.

17:02.012 --> 17:05.812
I can show you the designs to save time.

17:06.292 --> 17:06.772
Right?

17:07.413 --> 17:08.173
Look.

17:08.413 --> 17:11.252
We intend to make this set
our flagship product.

17:11.693 --> 17:12.413
And then...

17:14.572 --> 17:16.213
When a woman becomes unoffendable,

17:16.292 --> 17:18.133
unswayable, and unshakable,

17:18.893 --> 17:21.732
she develops an irresistible charm.

17:24.373 --> 17:24.893
Mr. Liang,

17:25.133 --> 17:27.213
your words flow like poetry.

17:28.012 --> 17:28.853
Remarkable.

17:29.012 --> 17:30.213
Neither of us is a fool.

17:31.133 --> 17:32.693
I know men like Shen Haoming

17:32.693 --> 17:34.133
born into affluent families.

17:34.732 --> 17:36.052
They never develop

17:36.052 --> 17:37.693
genuine emotional attachments.

17:38.492 --> 17:39.572
They're shallow

17:42.213 --> 17:43.173
and heartless.

17:43.373 --> 17:44.572
But when you're together,

17:44.772 --> 17:45.893
they make you feel

17:47.653 --> 17:48.653
deeply loved.

17:50.613 --> 17:52.252
You'd better free yourself from him.

17:52.693 --> 17:53.693
I'm willing to help.

17:53.812 --> 17:55.012
And I can be very generous.

17:55.092 --> 17:56.332
Please don't turn me down.

17:56.453 --> 17:56.973
I understand.

17:57.213 --> 17:58.213
I'm glad then.

17:58.373 --> 17:59.252
I'll surely become

17:59.252 --> 18:00.973
your most outstanding partner.

18:01.732 --> 18:02.492
I'll work hard.

18:03.052 --> 18:03.693
Trust me.

18:04.413 --> 18:05.133
Qiao Lin.

18:07.492 --> 18:08.532
Qiao Lin, listen.

18:08.732 --> 18:10.292
Set 1 and 3 have the same style.

18:10.292 --> 18:10.893
Charming.

18:11.213 --> 18:11.572
Yeah.

18:11.653 --> 18:12.572
I love it.

18:13.732 --> 18:14.373
Swap them.

18:14.693 --> 18:15.532
Okay, then.

18:15.772 --> 18:16.173
It's fine.

18:16.252 --> 18:17.092
Only earrings left.

18:17.133 --> 18:17.812
What about Guan?

18:17.812 --> 18:18.373
Same for her.

18:18.413 --> 18:19.492
This'll be quick.

18:20.853 --> 18:22.092
- I need to take this.
- Okay.

18:25.168 --> 18:26.352
(Shen Haoming)

18:31.812 --> 18:32.373
What's wrong?

18:35.532 --> 18:36.092
I'm busy.

18:38.332 --> 18:39.092
I'm busy.

18:39.572 --> 18:40.413
Okay, go ahead.

18:47.613 --> 18:48.173
Yan.

18:49.012 --> 18:49.613
Who was it?

18:51.173 --> 18:52.052
Shen Haoming.

18:52.693 --> 18:53.812
What does he want?

18:55.973 --> 18:56.653
(I need)

18:57.052 --> 18:57.893
(your help.)

18:59.492 --> 19:01.092
He needs my help with something.

19:02.532 --> 19:03.853
Things are so tense right now.

19:03.893 --> 19:05.092
Would he give you trouble?

19:10.812 --> 19:11.893
You want to see him?

19:13.092 --> 19:14.133
He reached out to me.

19:14.133 --> 19:15.653
It must be urgent.

19:16.413 --> 19:17.133
Don't worry.

19:17.492 --> 19:18.893
I'll handle it properly.

19:19.492 --> 19:20.213
Alright.

19:20.213 --> 19:21.173
Go then.

19:21.413 --> 19:22.693
You don't listen to anyone.

19:23.133 --> 19:24.012
But remember.

19:24.173 --> 19:25.933
Call me if anything happens.

19:27.213 --> 19:27.812
What for?

19:28.092 --> 19:28.973
I'll beat him up.

19:34.133 --> 19:35.492
Always so thoughtful.

19:36.693 --> 19:37.332
Go ahead.

19:37.893 --> 19:38.332
Right.

19:41.572 --> 19:42.012
Okay.

19:43.693 --> 19:44.893
Madam, hurry.

20:08.693 --> 20:09.173
Sit.

20:10.492 --> 20:11.532
It's been so long.

20:11.933 --> 20:12.492
How are you?

20:16.572 --> 20:17.252
I'm fine.

20:19.332 --> 20:20.373
How's your startup going?

20:22.613 --> 20:23.092
Sit.

20:32.292 --> 20:33.732
I'm not here for small talk.

20:36.213 --> 20:37.613
Just get to the point.

20:40.492 --> 20:41.933
I want to discuss a business deal.

20:43.373 --> 20:46.213
I know you're having funding issues.

20:47.012 --> 20:49.052
Consider this a fundraising opportunity.

20:55.332 --> 20:57.052
You're the one in bigger trouble.

20:58.492 --> 20:59.413
You asked me for help.

21:00.213 --> 21:02.613
So don't put on that superior act.

21:04.492 --> 21:05.973
Business requires sincerity.

21:18.893 --> 21:21.492
A Russian couple in real estate

21:22.693 --> 21:23.933
is arriving soon.

21:25.973 --> 21:27.973
I want to collaborate with them

21:28.492 --> 21:30.092
to expand our overseas markets.

21:31.292 --> 21:34.572
But the husband values family greatly.

21:35.853 --> 21:38.572
I hope we can appear in front of them

21:39.213 --> 21:40.492
as spouses.

21:41.693 --> 21:44.492
Help me gain their approval.

21:46.532 --> 21:47.732
Here's their profile.

21:51.732 --> 21:53.453
We're in the cooling-off period.

21:54.973 --> 21:56.693
We're not divorced yet.

21:57.173 --> 21:57.933
Legally,

21:58.613 --> 22:00.292
we're still married.

22:06.613 --> 22:08.213
I won't ask for free help.

22:09.453 --> 22:13.173
Feel free to state your terms.

22:25.296 --> 22:27.728
(Green Star Group Company Profile)

22:29.572 --> 22:30.893
How much do you make

22:32.012 --> 22:33.052
for sealing this deal?

22:34.613 --> 22:35.732
At least a billion.

22:47.693 --> 22:48.413
One million yuan.

22:54.252 --> 22:54.973
One million yuan?

22:55.092 --> 22:57.453
My help brings greater returns.

23:02.373 --> 23:03.572
If you refuse,

23:05.173 --> 23:06.173
find someone else.

23:08.373 --> 23:09.492
I meant to say

23:09.812 --> 23:11.052
the apparel industry requires

23:11.052 --> 23:12.012
heavy investment.

23:12.413 --> 23:14.532
A million alone won't make a splash.

23:16.893 --> 23:17.613
Here's the deal.

23:18.772 --> 23:20.973
I'll invest 10 million as a shareholder.

23:21.532 --> 23:23.492
I don't want your investment.

23:24.213 --> 23:25.812
This is an equal partnership.

23:26.133 --> 23:27.413
I'll only take my fee.

23:27.732 --> 23:29.812
I don't need anything else.

23:40.292 --> 23:40.772
Okay.

23:41.973 --> 23:42.893
Deal.

23:43.893 --> 23:45.973
One million yuan as your fee.

23:47.012 --> 23:48.413
But remember this.

23:48.653 --> 23:51.252
Mr. Baraikin values
marital bonds deeply.

23:51.653 --> 23:53.252
We need to look like

23:53.252 --> 23:55.012
the most loving couple.

23:58.332 --> 23:59.133
To our partnership.

24:03.492 --> 24:04.292
To our partnership.

24:31.772 --> 24:33.332
The outfit I picked for you look nice.

24:34.532 --> 24:35.213
Hello.

24:37.772 --> 24:38.332
Baby.

24:38.532 --> 24:39.572
Where are our IDs?

24:45.292 --> 24:46.213
Weren't you the one

24:46.213 --> 24:47.492
keeping them all along?

24:47.653 --> 24:49.213
My job is just to enjoy myself.

24:51.572 --> 24:52.292
It's my fault.

24:52.853 --> 24:53.893
I keep forgetting things.

24:54.492 --> 24:56.052
If we can't check in today,

24:56.292 --> 24:58.613
we'll have to camp outside.

24:58.772 --> 25:00.492
Then we'll sleep in a tent,

25:00.853 --> 25:02.213
watch stars and the moon,

25:02.292 --> 25:05.332
and have a barbecue.

25:07.213 --> 25:08.252
Sir, your room key.

25:08.332 --> 25:08.933
Thank you.

25:09.933 --> 25:10.453
Come on.

25:10.453 --> 25:12.812
This couple seems so in love.

25:13.492 --> 25:14.973
But I don't like Barbie.

25:15.133 --> 25:18.893
I prefer Twilight romance.

25:27.133 --> 25:27.973
Plan B.

26:14.252 --> 26:15.332
Excuse me.

26:20.893 --> 26:21.933
Excuse me.

26:28.052 --> 26:28.653
Look.

26:29.012 --> 26:30.973
These guys look like Edward and Bella.

26:31.052 --> 26:31.853
Yeah.

26:32.133 --> 26:34.532
That's my favorite love story.

26:34.772 --> 26:35.933
You used to watch it a lot.

26:35.933 --> 26:37.572
Yeah, once a week.

26:42.572 --> 26:43.173
Excuse me.

26:43.613 --> 26:44.332
Which floor?

26:50.973 --> 26:51.653
Same.

27:01.532 --> 27:02.173
Thank you.

27:06.012 --> 27:06.732
This way, please.

27:08.893 --> 27:10.492
Your room's at the end of this hall.

27:15.133 --> 27:16.252
Please give me a second.

27:16.893 --> 27:18.532
Excuse me, please.

27:20.413 --> 27:21.653
Thank you. This way, please.

27:28.933 --> 27:29.772
Almost there.

27:35.732 --> 27:36.492
Here.

27:42.693 --> 27:44.413
Enjoy your vacation.

27:51.292 --> 27:53.413
May I ask which room you're staying in?

27:55.173 --> 27:56.213
What floor is this?

27:57.052 --> 27:57.812
The second floor.

27:58.812 --> 27:59.952
We're on the third floor.

28:06.693 --> 28:07.653
Plan C.

28:50.572 --> 28:51.532
We have a room.

28:53.653 --> 28:54.173
Second floor.

28:55.572 --> 28:57.453
I wish you a pleasant stay.

28:58.492 --> 28:58.933
Please.

29:05.332 --> 29:06.772
Enjoy your stay.

29:07.492 --> 29:08.492
Thank you.

29:18.693 --> 29:19.252
Hello.

29:19.772 --> 29:22.173
Please send the priciest romance package

29:22.292 --> 29:23.492
to Room 2132.

29:24.092 --> 29:25.772
Make sure the cake says

29:25.933 --> 29:27.092
"I love you" on it.

29:27.772 --> 29:28.292
Thank you.

29:58.893 --> 29:59.453
Sir, your cake

29:59.572 --> 30:01.453
and champagne are here.

30:04.373 --> 30:06.973
But we didn't order this.

30:07.532 --> 30:07.973
But...

30:08.133 --> 30:10.292
This is Room 2132.

30:11.292 --> 30:12.653
It looks amazing.

30:12.973 --> 30:14.973
Honey, is this a surprise for me?

30:15.012 --> 30:16.252
Thank you, darling.

30:17.252 --> 30:18.092
Stop acting.

30:18.092 --> 30:19.133
I'm so happy.

30:20.332 --> 30:22.572
Please charge it to my room.

30:22.933 --> 30:24.092
Let me bring it inside.

30:24.092 --> 30:24.933
Thank you.

30:34.332 --> 30:34.772
He's gone.

30:55.532 --> 30:57.532
This cake is so good.

30:57.572 --> 30:58.973
Thank you, honey.

31:00.012 --> 31:01.732
Have more if you like it.

31:03.292 --> 31:03.772
Okay.

31:04.893 --> 31:05.292
Made it.

31:09.732 --> 31:10.252
Hello.

31:10.532 --> 31:11.292
May I help you?

31:11.973 --> 31:13.973
We ordered a romance package

31:14.373 --> 31:15.453
and I think the waiter

31:15.653 --> 31:17.012
brought it to your room.

31:17.933 --> 31:19.133
Oh, it was yours?

31:20.413 --> 31:21.413
I'm so sorry.

31:23.973 --> 31:25.092
We've already...

31:27.332 --> 31:29.532
I'm sorry, I already took a bite.

31:35.893 --> 31:36.613
I'm sorry, I...

31:36.613 --> 31:38.213
- Hello.
- I already took a bite.

31:42.133 --> 31:42.732
It's okay.

31:43.373 --> 31:44.492
No need to apologize.

31:45.853 --> 31:47.373
A beautiful cake like this

31:47.812 --> 31:49.453
is meant for a beautiful lady.

31:49.613 --> 31:50.133
Sorry.

31:50.613 --> 31:52.052
My wife seemed delighted.

31:52.092 --> 31:53.012
So we accepted it.

31:54.252 --> 31:54.973
I'm sorry.

31:55.292 --> 31:56.252
Me too.

31:57.812 --> 31:58.933
You are so in love.

31:59.292 --> 32:01.933
You're a great role model
for young couples like us.

32:04.012 --> 32:05.693
We won't disturb you. Let's go.

32:06.012 --> 32:06.693
Wait.

32:07.332 --> 32:09.772
How about the four of us share it?

32:09.812 --> 32:10.893
There's champagne too.

32:12.572 --> 32:13.693
This kind of cake

32:14.693 --> 32:15.893
is only meant for a couple.

32:16.853 --> 32:17.772
How about this, honey?

32:18.492 --> 32:19.213
Tonight,

32:19.572 --> 32:21.092
I'll take you to the hotel lawn.

32:22.133 --> 32:24.853
They're known for their shows.

32:26.133 --> 32:27.373
So romantic.

32:28.213 --> 32:29.492
You're also going to the lawn?

32:31.133 --> 32:33.893
Then let's have a drink later.

32:34.812 --> 32:35.492
- Okay.
- Okay.

32:36.252 --> 32:37.133
- See you tonight.
- See you tonight.

32:42.332 --> 32:43.052
Take the bed.

32:43.772 --> 32:44.532
I'll take the sofa.

32:44.653 --> 32:45.373
Okay, thanks.

32:56.532 --> 32:58.413
That cake was a good idea.

33:14.292 --> 33:15.532
Unpack your own stuff.

33:50.864 --> 33:54.608
â™ªI just wanna take my time tonightâ™ª

33:59.492 --> 34:00.092
Over here.

34:01.492 --> 34:02.092
Hello.

34:02.492 --> 34:03.973
- Good evening.
- Good evening.

34:04.893 --> 34:06.492
Let me introduce myself.

34:07.012 --> 34:08.212
I'm Shen Haoming.

34:09.333 --> 34:11.492
This is my wife, Xu Yan.

34:11.572 --> 34:12.413
I'm Baraikin.

34:12.492 --> 34:12.893
Hello.

34:13.052 --> 34:13.813
This is my wife.

34:13.893 --> 34:14.652
Hello.

34:15.652 --> 34:16.172
Over here.

34:16.172 --> 34:16.692
This way.

34:16.692 --> 34:18.532
- You speak fluent Chinese.
- What a nice dress.

34:18.853 --> 34:19.652
Horse-face skirt.

34:19.692 --> 34:20.973
I'll get you one if you like.

34:21.052 --> 34:21.893
Yes, please!

34:22.509 --> 34:25.222
â™ªWhen the time is rightâ™ª

34:26.853 --> 34:27.492
Perfect.

34:27.532 --> 34:28.652
Beautiful weather today.

34:29.212 --> 34:29.532
Indeed.

34:33.172 --> 34:33.520
Here.

34:33.612 --> 34:34.092
Thank you.

34:40.092 --> 34:40.652
Cheers.

34:40.813 --> 34:41.733
Cheers.

34:42.733 --> 34:44.333
After the wonderful performances,

34:44.492 --> 34:47.492
let's move on to the game session.

34:47.773 --> 34:49.893
Couples in Sync Challenge.

34:50.092 --> 34:51.492
We've prepared

34:51.492 --> 34:53.652
various games

34:53.893 --> 34:55.853
for couples.

34:56.172 --> 34:58.413
Let's see if you can
complete the challenges.

34:58.572 --> 34:59.893
Those who succeed

35:00.413 --> 35:02.373
will receive fabulous prizes.

35:02.692 --> 35:05.012
Who wants to go first

35:05.733 --> 35:07.652
and take the challenge?

35:09.652 --> 35:10.492
Excuse me.

35:10.532 --> 35:12.612
Why are you leaving?

35:12.893 --> 35:14.612
Are you scared that you might not

35:14.773 --> 35:15.773
be in sync?

35:16.492 --> 35:17.973
This looks fun. I want to try.

35:18.132 --> 35:18.612
Here.

35:19.773 --> 35:21.413
We have international guests too.

35:21.813 --> 35:23.652
Let's welcome them with applause.

35:28.132 --> 35:29.253
Let's try later too.

35:32.212 --> 35:33.933
It's called "Couples in Sync."

35:34.333 --> 35:35.293
How are we in sync?

35:35.853 --> 35:37.333
You Act, I Guess.

35:37.532 --> 35:38.933
Ready, go.

35:38.973 --> 35:40.532
Fine, then forget it.

35:41.253 --> 35:42.572
First question.

35:43.253 --> 35:43.973
Two words.

35:44.656 --> 35:46.128
(Sun Wukong)

35:46.492 --> 35:47.813
Let's see if you can guess it.

35:48.012 --> 35:48.733
(Sun Wukong)
Monkey.

35:49.652 --> 35:50.652
- Sun Wukong.
- Two words.

35:50.733 --> 35:52.373
Correct. Congratulations.

35:52.413 --> 35:53.172
Excellent.

35:53.172 --> 35:54.293
Alright, next question.

35:56.132 --> 35:56.532
Nice.

35:57.293 --> 35:58.492
Okay, two words.

36:01.733 --> 36:02.973
Show us your interpretation.

36:04.052 --> 36:05.532
Very vivid.

36:05.973 --> 36:06.692
(Giant Panda)
Two words.

36:07.052 --> 36:07.652
Big bear.

36:08.813 --> 36:09.652
Giant panda.

36:09.813 --> 36:11.492
Correct. Congratulations.

36:11.612 --> 36:12.692
Brilliant.

36:12.893 --> 36:13.773
Our foreign friend

36:13.773 --> 36:15.773
has a deep understanding
of Chinese culture.

36:16.012 --> 36:17.532
You're doing so well.

36:17.733 --> 36:18.853
We applaud you.

36:18.853 --> 36:19.373
Excellent.

36:19.413 --> 36:21.012
Okay, next question.

36:22.092 --> 36:23.052
Also two words.

36:24.733 --> 36:25.973
What's happening here?

36:27.212 --> 36:27.813
Okay.

36:30.172 --> 36:30.933
Dancing.

36:31.532 --> 36:32.492
Two words.

36:33.253 --> 36:33.893
Jump.

36:34.172 --> 36:34.733
What...

36:36.253 --> 36:36.973
Swing.

36:37.492 --> 36:38.212
Yangge dancing.

36:38.492 --> 36:40.092
Congratulations, that's correct.

36:40.612 --> 36:41.212
What is this?

36:41.212 --> 36:42.212
You got everything right.

36:42.373 --> 36:43.092
It's quite windy.

36:43.092 --> 36:43.572
Brilliant.

36:43.572 --> 36:44.853
Next question.

36:47.532 --> 36:48.132
Everyone.

36:48.492 --> 36:49.333
Two words.

36:49.373 --> 36:50.492
Still two words.

36:51.492 --> 36:52.212
There's no wind.

36:53.492 --> 36:55.413
Didn't you agree to cooperate?

36:56.052 --> 36:57.492
Why don't you try to appreciate

36:57.532 --> 36:58.492
your husband?

36:58.692 --> 36:59.973
Tai Chi.

37:00.413 --> 37:03.172
Congratulations again.

37:03.492 --> 37:04.492
A loving couple

37:04.492 --> 37:05.773
wouldn't show off in public.

37:06.212 --> 37:07.492
Don't you understand?

37:18.012 --> 37:18.933
The wife acting up

37:18.933 --> 37:20.132
is a part of the dynamic.

37:20.572 --> 37:21.572
Watch your attitude.

37:24.973 --> 37:27.373
You can act up,
but don't cross the line, okay?

37:30.572 --> 37:31.333
Are you upset?

37:32.893 --> 37:34.092
Replace me then.

37:34.572 --> 37:35.532
I'll just quit.

37:36.413 --> 37:38.733
Don't forget we have a contract.

37:40.333 --> 37:41.612
It's mutually binding.

37:42.212 --> 37:43.492
I'm not your subordinate.

37:43.733 --> 37:46.092
Don't order me around like before.

37:50.253 --> 37:51.933
Congratulations, that's correct.

37:52.492 --> 37:53.492
Amazing.

37:53.973 --> 37:55.373
They're so in sync.

37:55.373 --> 37:55.773
Okay.

37:55.813 --> 37:57.933
Let's proceed to the next part.

37:58.212 --> 37:58.933
Bring the towels.

38:07.933 --> 38:09.572
Unentangle the towels.

38:09.572 --> 38:10.893
It's a simple game.

38:11.092 --> 38:12.333
Let's see what happens.

38:12.333 --> 38:14.293
It's impossible to communicate with you.

38:14.373 --> 38:16.132
Then let's stop communicating.

38:17.492 --> 38:18.733
Focus on your task.

38:18.733 --> 38:20.652
Another round of applause for them!

38:22.172 --> 38:24.012
Why do you think we're getting divorced?

38:24.893 --> 38:26.893
If you can't find the right approach,

38:27.293 --> 38:28.492
try different methods.

38:30.373 --> 38:32.052
Try different approaches

38:32.092 --> 38:33.893
to get the towels unentangled.

38:33.893 --> 38:35.212
Because you used me.

38:37.773 --> 38:38.692
Didn't you use me?

38:38.893 --> 38:40.253
But I truly love you.

38:47.212 --> 38:48.212
Loved you.

38:50.773 --> 38:51.692
I helped you too.

38:52.172 --> 38:53.492
That means, to you,

38:53.492 --> 38:55.692
our relationship was nothing

38:55.692 --> 38:58.413
but a transaction all along, right?

38:58.612 --> 39:00.773
I don't think we need to
reach this point.

39:00.773 --> 39:01.612
What do you mean?

39:02.813 --> 39:03.612
Want to reconcile?

39:08.532 --> 39:09.612
I've tried.

39:10.293 --> 39:10.973
Did it work?

39:14.933 --> 39:15.692
It's too late.

39:16.492 --> 39:17.612
I just want to tell you

39:17.692 --> 39:19.893
that being with me will benefit you.

39:20.012 --> 39:21.092
Your current business

39:21.132 --> 39:22.293
will waste your money.

39:22.333 --> 39:23.532
Only I can save you, okay?

39:23.532 --> 39:24.853
Why do you overestimate yourself?

39:25.492 --> 39:26.973
And why do you belittle me?

39:28.853 --> 39:30.293
You think no one wants to fund me?

39:30.652 --> 39:31.413
Listen carefully.

39:31.612 --> 39:33.652
Investors are lining up.

39:33.973 --> 39:34.813
Want to invest?

39:35.253 --> 39:36.052
Get in line.

39:37.293 --> 39:38.352
Who's investing in you?

39:39.853 --> 39:40.492
Tell me.

39:40.652 --> 39:41.532
Stop talking.

39:42.733 --> 39:43.293
Yan.

39:46.373 --> 39:47.652
Look, this is my trophy.

39:47.933 --> 39:48.893
So cute.

39:48.933 --> 39:49.492
Yeah.

39:49.572 --> 39:51.212
Would you like to give it a try?

39:51.212 --> 39:51.612
It's fun.

39:51.612 --> 39:52.172
Us?

39:52.373 --> 39:53.373
It's really fun.

39:54.853 --> 39:55.813
Want to try, honey?

39:59.092 --> 39:59.612
Alright.

40:00.373 --> 40:01.733
The next game is called:

40:01.733 --> 40:03.172
"Which Way to Look?

40:03.253 --> 40:04.293
One, Two, Three."

40:04.652 --> 40:06.333
It's another test to see if the couples

40:06.333 --> 40:07.373
are in sync.

40:07.652 --> 40:09.853
Please listen to my command.

40:10.012 --> 40:11.012
After I say,

40:11.253 --> 40:13.052
"Which way to look? One, two, three,"

40:13.132 --> 40:14.612
turn your heads.

40:14.893 --> 40:16.933
If you turn in the same direction,

40:16.973 --> 40:17.773
you win.

40:17.933 --> 40:20.813
Otherwise, you will
receive a punishment.

40:21.132 --> 40:21.652
Now,

